Class Channel

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.timmyrs.suprdiscordbot.structures.Structure
      • de.timmyrs.suprdiscordbot.structures.Channel

  • public class Channel
extends Structure
    Channel Structure. You can retrieve an array of channel structures using Guild.getChannels() and DiscordAPI.getDMs().

    timmyRS

        public Message[] getMessages(int count)
